OL,3,CGovernment set to ban wet wipes
OL,4,Ccontaining plastic to fight water
OL,5,Cpollution
OL,7,FWet wipes containing plastic are set
OL,8,Fto be banned from sale in the UK under
OL,9,Flegislation expected to be confirmed
OL,10,Fon Monday.
OL,12,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Barclay is
OL,13,Fexpected to announce plans to
OL,14,Fintroduce legislation before the
OL,15,Fsummer recess in July following a long-
OL,16,Frunning campaign to ban the products.
OL,18,FThe law would make it illegal to sell
OL,19,For supply wet wipes containing plastic
OL,20,Fin England, with the rest of the UK
OL,21,Fset to follow by the autumn.
