OL,7,FWet wipes eventually break down into
OL,8,Fmicroplastics, which damage ecosystems
OL,9,Fand contribute to water pollution, and
OL,10,Fdiscarded wipes have increasingly
OL,11,Flittered Britain's beaches.
OL,13,FMr Barclay said: "I have been clear
OL,14,Fthat a step change is needed to
OL,15,Fprotect our waterways from pollution.
