OL,7,F"The ban builds on a raft of actions
OL,8,Falready taken to protect our waterways
OL,9,Fand hold water companies accountable,
OL,10,Fincluding accelerating investment,
OL,11,Fputting water company fines back into
OL,12,Fthe environment and quadrupling the
OL,13,Fnumber of inspections of water company
OL,14,Fsites."
OL,16,FBut Labour said the ban did not go far
OL,17,Fenough, committing to a "a full ban on
OL,18,Fthe sale, supply and manufacture of
OL,19,Fplastic wet wipes".
