OL,7,FShadow environment secretary Steve
OL,8,FReed said: "Plastic wet wipes clog up
OL,9,Four sewers, kill wildlife and lead to
OL,10,Fsewage backing up into people's homes.
OL,12,F"The Conservatives have broken their
OL,13,Fpromises to act and are too weak to
OL,14,Fban them outright."
OL,16,FThe party also pointed out that the
OL,17,FConservatives had first promised to
OL,18,Fban wet wipes in 2018 as part of a
OL,19,Fcrackdown on plastic waste.
