OL,7,FMonday's proposals follow a
OL,8,Fconsultation that saw overwhelming
OL,9,Fsupport for the move.
OL,11,FA previous consultation, in 2021, also
OL,12,Ffound more than 90% of people were in
OL,13,Ffavour of a ban.
OL,15,FSome businesses such as Boots, Aldi
OL,16,Fand Tesco have already moved to ban
OL,17,Fwet wipes containing plastics from
OL,18,Ftheir stores.
